{"id":226,"parent_id":224,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":226,"title":"Hebrews 2","subtitle":"","short_title":"Heb.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 2"],[".studySummary",["i","Jesus came to suffer death and save men—He came to make reconciliation for the sins of the people."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.1","order":"03.21.002.23409"},["b","1"],"Therefore we ought to give the more",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"earnest"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"heed"],"to the things which we have heard, lest at any time we should let",["i","them"],"slip."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.2","order":"03.21.002.23410"},["b","2"],"For if the word spoken by angels was steadfast, and every transgression and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"disobedience"],"received a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"just"],"recompence of reward;"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.3","order":"03.21.002.23411"},["b","3"],"How shall we",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"escape"],", if we neglect so great salvation; which at the first began to be spoken by the Lord, and was confirmed unto us by them that heard",["i","him;"]],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.4","order":"03.21.002.23412"},["b","4"],"God also bearing",["i","them"],"witness, both with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"signs"],"and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"wonders"],", and with divers miracles, and gifts of the Holy Ghost, according to his own",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"will"],"?"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.5","order":"03.21.002.23413"},["b","5"],"For unto the angels hath he not put in subjection the world to come, whereof we speak."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.6","order":"03.21.002.23414"},["b","6"],"But one in a certain place testified, saying, What is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"man"],", that thou art mindful of him? or the son of man, that thou visitest him?"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.7","order":"03.21.002.23415"},["b","7"],"Thou madest him a little lower than the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"angels"],"; thou crownedst him with glory and honour, and didst set him over the works of thy hands:"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.8","order":"03.21.002.23416"},["b","8"],"Thou hast put all things in subjection under his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"feet"],". For in that he put all in subjection under him, he left nothing",["i","that is"],"not put under him. But now we see not yet all things put under him."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.9","order":"03.21.002.23417"},["b","9"],"But we see Jesus, who was made a little",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"lower"],"than the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"angels"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"for"],"the suffering of",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_9d"},"death"],",",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_9e"},"crowned"],"with glory and honour; that he by the",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_9f"},"grace"],"of God should taste",["sup","g"],["a",{"href":"fn_9g"},"death"],"for every man."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.10","order":"03.21.002.23418"},["b","10"],"For",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"it became him"],", for whom",["i","are"],"all things, and by whom",["i","are"],"all",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"things"],", in bringing many sons unto glory, to make the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"captain"],"of their salvation",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"perfect"],"through sufferings."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.11","order":"03.21.002.23419"},["b","11"],"For both he that sanctifieth and they who are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"sanctified"],["i","are"],"all of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"one"],": for which cause he is not ashamed to call them",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"brethren"],","],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.12","order":"03.21.002.23420"},["b","12"],"Saying, I will declare thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"name"],"unto my brethren, in the midst of the church will I sing praise unto thee."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.13","order":"03.21.002.23421"},["b","13"],"And again, I will put my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"trust"],"in him. And again, Behold I and the children which God hath given me."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.14","order":"03.21.002.23422"},["b","14"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Forasmuch then as"],"the children are partakers of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"flesh and blood"],", he also himself likewise took part of the same; that through death he might",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"destroy"],"him that had the power of",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_14d"},"death"],", that is, the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_14e"},"devil"],";"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.15","order":"03.21.002.23423"},["b","15"],"And deliver them who through fear of death were all their lifetime subject to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"bondage"],"."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.16","order":"03.21.002.23424"},["b","16"],"For verily he took not on",["i","him the nature of"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"angels"],"; but he took on",["i","him"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"seed of Abraham"],"."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.17","order":"03.21.002.23425"},["b","17"],"Wherefore in all things it behoved him to be made like unto",["i","his"],"brethren, that he might be a merciful and faithful high priest in things",["i","pertaining"],"to God, to make",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"reconciliation"],"for the sins of the people."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.18","order":"03.21.002.23426"},["b","18"],"For in that he himself hath suffered being",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"tempted"],", he is able to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"succour"],"them that are tempted."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.1a","order":"03.21.002.23427"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zeal"},"TG Zeal"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.1b","order":"03.21.002.23429"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/21.4"},"D&C 21:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.2a","order":"03.21.002.23431"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/disobedience"},"TG Disobedience"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.2b","order":"03.21.002.23433"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-justice-of"},"TG God, Justice of"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.3a","order":"03.21.002.23435"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.29"},"Heb. 10:29"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/12.25"},"12:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.4a","order":"03.21.002.23437"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/5.12.12-23"},"Acts 5:12 (12–23)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-gifts-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Gifts of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/symbolism"},"Symbolism"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.4b","order":"03.21.002.23439"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/miracle"},"TG Miracle"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.4c","order":"03.21.002.23441"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-will-of"},"TG God, Will of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.6a","order":"03.21.002.23443"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/8.4.4-6"},"Ps. 8:4 (4–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.7a","order":"03.21.002.23445"},["b","7a"],["span.small","HEB"],"gods;",["span.small","GR"],"angels."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.8a","order":"03.21.002.23447"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.18"},"Matt. 28:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/15.25"},"1 Cor. 15:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/1.22"},"Eph. 1:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.9a","order":"03.21.002.23449"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-condescension-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Condescension of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.9b","order":"03.21.002.23451"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.7.7-9"},"Philip. 2:7 (7–9)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.9c","order":"03.21.002.23453"},["b","9c"],["span.small","GR"],"through."],["div",{"id":"9d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.9d","order":"03.21.002.23455"},["b","9d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-death-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Death of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.9e","order":"03.21.002.23457"},["b","9e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/2.33"},"Acts 2:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"9f","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.9f","order":"03.21.002.23459"},["b","9f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/grace"},"TG Grace"],"."],["div",{"id":"9g","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.9g","order":"03.21.002.23461"},["b","9g"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-atonement-through"},"TG Jesus Christ, Atonement through"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.10a","order":"03.21.002.23463"},["b","10a"],["span.small","GR"],"it was fitting, suitable, proper for Him."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.10b","order":"03.21.002.23465"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/1.16.13-19"},"Col. 1:16 (13–19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.10c","order":"03.21.002.23467"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-messiah"},"TG Jesus Christ, Messiah"],"."],["div",{"id":